        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         To steal a phrase from Michael Pollan\xe2\x80\x99s bestselling 2018 book on the benefits of psychedelics, I want you to
         <em>
          <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFULluwzAM_ZposyHJko9BQxGgW7cunQzaYh0hNmXoqOF-fZVkKECQ4PH4yDdDwsWH0-w-JpYjhtFZI1rZN1oNzBplRa975uL4HRA3cKtJISPb87S6GZLz9ERwLjW7GSVFq7vvjnOY2hkGrjqB7dTqFqToVMEVnhGydUgzGvzBcHpCtppbSnu8NG8X-V7sOI4aNvj1VM9-K4XrDWjB6svnUH04stXVU5ydz5EwxuozQEmR7GNtGbd7cUIPSnIly2XOSC65EHwQje4bWYtaU1iOAGKyeFF8W2Qd8xQTzPcHJQuGfJp8cLSU9v0GG67PRvl8LHHL5NI5IsG0on2Jkl4yPn9M546G8IgrpoThVXwo1fNByq5jhc36Iij9E_0Bz8qHMQ" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
           Change Your Mind
          </a>
         </em>
         . By the end of this essay, you\xe2\x80\x99ll understand why we underestimate psychedelics, the promise they hold in solving our biggest mental health challenges, and the business model behind the first public psychedelics company in the US, COMPASS Pathways.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         It\xe2\x80\x99s easy to get excited about psychedelics. MDMA combined with therapy looks like it may cure PTSD in a large number of patients. Psilocybin with therapy is showing promise in fighting depression. And unlike traditional medication, psychedelics can cure while creating meaning. In a
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkMGKxCAQRL9mPIbWJDPx4GEv8xvBaJs0Y1TUbMjfrzNzWGgoqKIp6hldcY35UimWyo6CeSar-F1M_ThIZtVg-TROjMrsMuKuyauaD2TpWDwZXSmGzweAGNmmXA-uH-EhpRu4kWBACAuTvkstrAPD3j2zPixhMKjwF_MVAzKvtlpTufU_N_Fsd55nt8X0olB2tGQoYBfz2pKUsZQ5o0ddsDRDANybrJmco7qVVMhHcy0UumQdIyVAAOcgeT9Oveh4N4a8nlnzxeJtgH0VXTmWUrV5dSbuLKsQ6xIzhbXFr03v6D9B2zw33Y9A9Zox6MWj_eKoX4CfdfVKqAKexWOtmL_mm9EEUojHg7U2GxvK8F_0B52Ph60" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          2006 Johns Hopkins study
         </a>
         , 67% of participants who took psilocybin rated the experience either the most meaningful or among the top five most meaningful in their lives! As Matthew Johnson, the Associate Director of the Johns Hopkins Center for Psychedelic and Consciousness Research
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkMGugyAQRb-m7DCA2uqCxdu83zAIUyVVMMNY49-_sV28hADhzsy9HO8Ipoyn3XIhsRfAIQar76ar26YXwTZBd20nYhmeCLC6uFjCHcS2j0v0jmJOnw6lTCtmWzdd02rXBP80da9Uf2-0Cvc2eF_3znXi8hncHiIkDxbegGdOIBY7E23lVv_czC-v4ziq4rmI4pNtVkDeU-XzyqJDin4BvtEMCEWmLKecg4R3DNdcSbMjuZXTzxCAcxbJ3dLPLk0gz7yj3PIS6RIySuSSiT_CA0W0Rhmltep13Xa1qXTVJpwOdHoMcGvUOpmq7GMh519XHoE2ZRozxjSx_Jo57PIRGNHA57qnSOcAyY0LhC89-vL-wKBzA5vgKAsQAX4fL6Sd6o15PAS7hczk07_RH_TemWs" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          wrote
         </a>
         , \xe2\x80\x9cPsychedelics are psychoactive substances that historically have attracted exaggerations of benefits as well as alarmism.\xe2\x80\x9d
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         So let\xe2\x80\x99s try to avoid exaggerations, and instead take a trip together to soberly explore:
        </p>
        <ul style="margin: 1em 0;">
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           <strong>
            The Psychedelic Renaissance.
           </strong>
           After fifty years, psychedelics are going mainstream again.
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           <strong>
            The War On Drugs.
           </strong>
           Like the Food Pyramid, but Drugs.
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           <strong>
            Mushrooms\xe2\x80\x99 Magic.
           </strong>
           Although there are many promising psychedelic compounds, we\xe2\x80\x99ll focus mainly on psilocybin given its potential wide-ranging benefits.
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           <strong>
            COMPASS\xe2\x80\x99 Pathway.
           </strong>
           The story behind the first public psychedelic company.
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           <strong>
            COMPASS\xe2\x80\x99 Business Model.
           </strong>
           COMPASS is like a dating app -- it\xe2\x80\x99s product may be so good that it\xe2\x80\x99s bad for business. But analysts are bullish, and so am I.
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">
           <strong>
            Irrational Exuberance About Psychedelics\xe2\x80\x99 Future.
           </strong>
           Can they make the world a more harmonious place? Can they unleash creativity? Can they cure everything?
          </p>
         </li>
        </ul>
