          </table>
         </figure>
        </div>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         When Harper\xe2\x80\x99s writer Dan Baum tracked Nixon\xe2\x80\x99s domestic policy chief John Ehrlichman down in 1994, Erlichman
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUMuOwyAM_Jpy24hHaMmBw172NyIeJkElEBnSKvv1S9vDSpYfY1ujGWcaLAVPvZfayFEB5-g1u3Il5DgRr0fPlFQk1jkgwGZi0g0PIPthU3SmxZLfH5RySVY9jXCzwYVAg5mEdMoEp64TFUzwYKUlL57ZHD5CdqDhAXiWDCTptbW9XsT3hf_0WA3ugHUouPTJoFvjA3rHKbv2QseeEiwmxV_4iu3LpNQREjWn_YTRiQmpBB_YIDMuTzTMeriMdFv4UA9bm3H3wZWNoM6l2YIxL319X80G6b3oAudetyPHds6QjU3gP9rbx623lHbuoDM8a4LWAD_gyxBFJ85vN9LZfOm-5X-iP1rafps" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          admitted
         </a>
         that the War on Drugs was an indirect way to target the two enemies of the Nixon administration: the antiwar movement and Black people. \xe2\x80\x9cDid we know we were lying about drugs? Of course we did.\xe2\x80\x9d
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         In a total narc move, the US also pushed other countries to follow its drug scheduling guidelines. The 1971 UN treaty, the Convention on Psychotropic Substances, largely adopted the US scheduling, grouping psilocybin with drugs like heroin and crack cocaine and effectively halting research on its benefits worldwide.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Despite being built atop a lie, the War on Drugs and its associated propaganda worked for decades. It\xe2\x80\x99s why we\xe2\x80\x99re just getting back to psychedelics now.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         When I was in 7th grade, we had to read a book. I forget what it was called or what it was about; the only thing I remember is that the main character\xe2\x80\x99s older brother did acid once, lived in a flop house, and had frequent flashbacks in which spiders crawled all over his body for years.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         It surprised me to find out many years and \xe2\x80\x9cno acid for me, thanks!\xe2\x80\x9ds later that LSD and mushrooms are the two safest drugs out there on the active/lethal dose and dependence potential scale. All weekend, I was drinking beers and coffee; turns out I would have been much safer tripping.
        </p>
